pokedexEntries.gold: Its body has been compressed deep under the ground. As a result, it is even harder than a diamond.
pokedexEntries.silver: It is said that if an Onix lives for over 100 years, its composition changes to become diamond-like.
pokedexEntries.crystal: The many small metal particles that cover this Pokémon's body reflect bright light well.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Steelix lives even further underground than Onix. This Pokémon is known to dig towards the earth's core. There are records of this Pokémon reaching a depth of over six-tenths of a mile underground.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Steelix lives even further underground than Onix. This Pokémon is known to dig towards the earth's core. There are records of this Pokémon reaching a depth of over six-tenths of a mile underground.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Steelix live even further underground than Onix. This Pokémon is known to dig toward the earth's core, reaching a depth of over six-tenths of a mile underground.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It is said that if an Onix lives for over 100 years, its composition changes to become diamond-like.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Its body has been compressed deep under the ground. As a result, it is even harder than a diamond.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Tempered underground under high pressure and heat, its body is harder than any metal.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It chews its way through boulders with its sturdy jaws. Its eyes can see in the dark underground.
pokedexEntries.platinum: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: Its body has been compressed deep under the ground. As a result, it is even harder than a diamond.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: It is said that if an Onix lives for 100 years, its composition becomes diamondlike as it evolves into a Steelix.
pokedexEntries.black: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.
pokedexEntries.white: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.
pokedexEntries.black2: The iron it ingested with the soil it swallowed transformed its body and made it harder than diamonds.
pokedexEntries.white2: The iron it ingested with the soil it swallowed transformed its body and made it harder than diamonds.
pokedexEntries.x: Tempered underground under high pressure and heat, its body is harder than any metal.
pokedexEntries.y: It chews its way through boulders with its sturdy jaws. Its eyes can see in the darkness underground.
